1:02:22.322 --> 1:02:24.366
I'm all the stud you need.

1:02:29.747 --> 1:02:30.664
Where's Lisa?

1:02:30.998 --> 1:02:32.332
Let it go, Nicky.

1:02:32.666 --> 1:02:33.834
It's too late.

1:02:37.463 --> 1:02:38.881
Out of my way, Claudia.

1:02:39.214 --> 1:02:40.507
Forget it, Nicky.

1:02:41.216 --> 1:02:43.510
Charlie wants this one real bad.

1:02:43.844 --> 1:02:46.346
We've got enough problems in this dorm.

1:02:46.680 --> 1:02:47.848
It ain't our fight no more.

1:02:48.182 --> 1:02:49.600
God damn it, she's just a kid.

1:02:49.933 --> 1:02:52.019
- She's helpless.
- That's right.

1:02:52.352 --> 1:02:57.399
Maybe what she needs is what Charlie
can give her, some protection.

1:02:58.567 --> 1:03:00.444
Now, we take on Charlie, we take on Edna.

1:03:02.154 --> 1:03:03.363
Let her have the kid.

1:03:06.909 --> 1:03:08.202
Welcome to the club.

1:03:14.833 --> 1:03:17.044
It's a perfect job.

1:03:32.267 --> 1:03:33.644
My God.

1:03:36.647 --> 1:03:39.900
Why is the condition of this girl so bad?

1:03:40.234 --> 1:03:43.362
It ain't easy to make yourself
pretty in the hole.

1:03:45.405 --> 1:03:49.034
Jenny, nobody even told me you were in
until this morning.

1:03:49.368 --> 1:03:51.662
God, Jenny, you look terrible.

1:03:51.995 --> 1:03:54.373
I'm fine.
Thanks for the water.

1:03:54.790 --> 1:03:57.000
You know, your time's been doubled.

1:03:57.334 --> 1:04:00.170
I can't believe it, Jenny.
You want to tell me what's happened?

1:04:00.504 --> 1:04:01.922
