1:04:02.256 --> 1:04:05.592
Their version is, but I want to hear
what you've got to say.

1:04:05.926 --> 1:04:07.469
Nothing I say counts.

1:04:07.803 --> 1:04:10.180
What you've got there in my file
is all that matters.

1:04:10.514 --> 1:04:12.766
Everything's done by the book, right, doc?

1:04:13.308 --> 1:04:15.435
I'm going to do something else
by the book, Jenny.

1:04:15.769 --> 1:04:18.480
I'm filing a report
to the Youth Authority Commission.

1:04:18.814 --> 1:04:22.693
Now, this could get serious.
Sutter will obviously oppose my position.

1:04:23.026 --> 1:04:24.236
I want you to testify.

1:04:24.570 --> 1:04:26.655
Tell how you
and the other girls are treated,

1:04:26.989 --> 1:04:29.241
how you've been abused here.

1:04:29.575 --> 1:04:31.076
I'm no pigeon.

1:04:31.618 --> 1:04:34.872
You think I'm going to stick my neck out
on the block so you can hand Edna the axe?

1:04:35.205 --> 1:04:37.541
Jenny, I'll protect you.

1:04:37.875 --> 1:04:41.128
I won't let anything happen to you,
but I can't do it alone.

1:04:41.461 --> 1:04:46.466
I need positive evidence, solid testimony,
anything that'll help me present my case.

1:04:46.967 --> 1:04:49.344
Can't you see what I'm after, Jenny?

1:04:49.678 --> 1:04:50.554
Listen, doc.

1:04:50.888 --> 1:04:52.931
I know you mean well, but so far,
there's been a lot of talk

1:04:53.265 --> 1:04:54.266
and a lot of pain.

1:04:54.600 --> 1:04:57.644
The talk doesn't seem to change much,
but the pain sure makes you think.

1:04:58.854 --> 1:05:00.272
I'll see you around.

1:05:23.795 --> 1:05:26.131
Sure feels good to clean up
after two weeks in that hole.

1:05:26.465 --> 1:05:29.968
- How's it going for you, kid?
- Oh, I'm okay now.

1:05:30.510 --> 1:05:33.513
Nicky told me what happened.
Wouldn't have happened if I was here.

1:05:33.847 --> 1:05:35.599
I know, thanks.

1:05:36.725 --> 1:05:40.145
Hey, I heard number 11 had
a flop out last night.

1:05:40.729 --> 1:05:42.522
She got it worse than you.

1:05:42.856 --> 1:05:44.316
Two cut wrists going over the fence.

1:05:44.650 --> 1:05:46.652
What difference does it make?

1:05:46.985 --> 1:05:48.403
She was a wanker.

1:05:48.904 --> 1:05:50.864
You're all wankers.

1:05:51.281 --> 1:05:54.493
This place was running smooth
until you ingrates

1:05:54.826 --> 1:05:56.703
started messing things up.

1:05:57.037 --> 1:06:02.459
This place ain't never run smooth
but for no one but you, Charlie.

1:06:02.793 --> 1:06:07.255
I'm through taking the hard labor shit
for you guys.

1:06:07.589 --> 1:06:09.299
We're through taking shit from Edna

1:06:09.633 --> 1:06:11.843
so you can get your way around here,
princess.

1:06:12.177 --> 1:06:15.138
Come on,
let's beat the shit out of each other.

1:06:15.472 --> 1:06:17.099
Your time's already doubled.

1:06:17.432 --> 1:06:19.768
Let's see if we can get it tripled.
Come on.

1:06:20.769 --> 1:06:23.522
She ain't worth getting busted over.

1:06:23.855 --> 1:06:26.233
You know Edna
won't take our side over hers. Come on.

1:06:28.318 --> 1:06:31.738
Line up. Countdown.

1:06:41.873 --> 1:06:43.125
All right.

1:06:43.458 --> 1:06:45.460
Let's play the name game.

1:06:45.794 --> 1:06:46.837
Charmin, Karen.

1:06:47.170 --> 1:06:48.171
Eldrige, Andrea.

1:06:48.505 --> 1:06:49.631
Stewart, Lisa.

1:06:49.965 --> 1:06:51.341
Chambliss, Charlie.

1:06:51.675 --> 1:06:52.634
Williams, Jennifer.

1:06:52.968 --> 1:06:54.261
Adams, Nicky.

1:07:19.411 --> 1:07:20.829
What the hell was that?

1:07:21.246 --> 1:07:23.415
No, no!

1:07:23.749 --> 1:07:26.251
- Give me that!
- No!

1:07:59.618 --> 1:08:04.623
Who dared to bring this animal in here?

1:08:05.082 --> 1:08:10.462
I said,
who dared to bring this animal in here?

1:08:14.883 --> 1:08:16.093
All right.

1:08:16.468 --> 1:08:18.053
Have it your own way.

1:08:18.678 --> 1:08:23.058
If I don't have the name of every girl
responsible for this by morning,

1:08:24.017 --> 1:08:25.644
you'll all pay.

1:08:28.647 --> 1:08:33.735
Just don't stand there,
bring me something to wipe my shoe.

1:09:07.519 --> 1:09:08.895
Oh, my God. Lisa.

1:09:09.479 --> 1:09:10.856
Lisa? Where?

1:09:17.696 --> 1:09:19.865
Oh, my God, she's going to kill herself.

1:09:21.575 --> 1:09:23.160
You little bitch.

1:09:23.493 --> 1:09:25.954
You start trouble all the time.

1:09:26.288 --> 1:09:28.748
I'm going to really fuck with you.

1:09:31.835 --> 1:09:38.133
Lisa!

1:09:38.592 --> 1:09:41.761
Not one more step, do you hear me?
Not one more step!

1:09:42.095 --> 1:09:43.972
Hold on, damn it.

1:09:46.683 --> 1:09:49.686
Not one more step.
Not one more step.

1:09:50.020 --> 1:09:54.983
You stop right there.

1:09:58.862 --> 1:10:01.573
I'm going to kill you
once I get my hands on you.

1:10:04.284 --> 1:10:06.036
You're going to pay for this, young lady.

1:10:06.369 --> 1:10:08.121
You're going to pay for this.

1:10:08.455 --> 1:10:10.207
Don't you dare move away from me.

1:10:16.171 --> 1:10:21.760
Oh, my God.

1:12:09.159 --> 1:12:11.286
Not one word.

1:12:11.911 --> 1:12:13.663
I'll get to the bottom of this setup.

1:12:14.039 --> 1:12:16.207
- You can be sure.
- Shut up.

1:12:17.125 --> 1:12:18.793
It was them.
They did it.

1:12:19.210 --> 1:12:20.837
Back in your cage.

1:12:21.379 --> 1:12:24.090
There's no sucking up to Edna this time.

1:12:25.467 --> 1:12:27.135
You. Look at you.

1:12:27.844 --> 1:12:30.221
I thought you were going
to whip this place into shape.

1:12:30.972 --> 1:12:33.266
I should have known
I'd have to do it myself.

1:12:34.434 --> 1:12:36.561
- Your time is doubled.
- So's your chin.

1:12:37.020 --> 1:12:38.063
Tripled.

1:12:38.396 --> 1:12:40.273
Who's dishing out the shit around here,
Edna?

1:12:40.607 --> 1:12:41.900
You were queen mother.

1:12:42.317 --> 1:12:45.403
Charlie, you're nothing but a stupid kid
from Cleveland,

1:12:45.820 --> 1:12:48.156
just a shit stain
on the panties of life.

1:12:48.531 --> 1:12:51.159
You should know,
you lick 'em every night.

1:12:51.534 --> 1:12:54.412
No privileges until further notice,
and clean up this dump.

1:12:59.793 --> 1:13:01.252
Party's over, kid.

1:13:01.878 --> 1:13:03.213
Take her away.

1:13:05.840 --> 1:13:08.218
I'll piss on your grave, fuck!

1:13:14.599 --> 1:13:17.185
Two weeks in the hole wasn't enough,
I see.

1:13:17.644 --> 1:13:18.895
You fucking killer.

1:13:19.270 --> 1:13:20.939
Killer?

1:13:21.481 --> 1:13:24.317
You'll wish I had killed you
before I'm done.

1:13:32.075 --> 1:13:33.952
Get out of them clothes.

1:13:34.285 --> 1:13:35.912
Get them off, now.

1:13:37.330 --> 1:13:39.791
Get those clothes off.
Get them off.

1:13:47.757 --> 1:13:53.430
Now, I know who was behind all of this,
but I want to hear it from you.

1:13:55.348 --> 1:14:00.645
I want the name of every girl
who took part in this tonight,

1:14:00.979 --> 1:14:03.440
and I want to hear you say it loud.

1:14:03.815 --> 1:14:08.236
No, no, no, no,

1:14:08.820 --> 1:14:14.242
no, no, no, no!

1:14:21.791 --> 1:14:24.752
Say it, damn you. Say it.

1:14:28.089 --> 1:14:31.134
Say it, damn you. Say it.

1:14:31.468 --> 1:14:34.137
Say it, damn you. Say it.

1:14:34.471 --> 1:14:39.309
Say it! Say it, damn you! Say it!

1:14:39.976 --> 1:14:43.646
Damn you! Say it! Say it!

1:14:44.022 --> 1:14:47.066
Damn you! Say it!

1:14:49.444 --> 1:14:52.739
- What the hell is going on here, Sutter?
- What now?

1:14:53.198 --> 1:14:55.575
- I want answers and I want them fast.
- Whoa, there.

1:14:55.909 --> 1:14:57.827
No!
You "whoa," damn it.

1:14:58.244 --> 1:15:00.371
Now, I'm away from this place
for three days.

1:15:00.705 --> 1:15:05.043
One girl commits suicide,
two are in solitary, and a third
is unconscious

1:15:05.376 --> 1:15:07.420
in the infirmary, unable
to tell me what's happening.

1:15:07.754 --> 1:15:09.172
Now, I want answers.

1:15:09.714 --> 1:15:11.341
I don't take to threats.

1:15:11.674 --> 1:15:14.969
You'd better take to this one, Sutter,
because when I file my report

1:15:15.303 --> 1:15:16.930
to the youth commission,
you're going to be answering

1:15:17.263 --> 1:15:18.598
to more than just threats.

1:15:23.853 --> 1:15:25.146
Norton's history.

1:15:25.897 --> 1:15:28.024
I want her off the premises at once.

1:15:29.108 --> 1:15:30.652
Give me the commission.

1:15:38.618 --> 1:15:40.370
Don't leave us now, doc.

1:15:41.079 --> 1:15:43.998
You were right,
we need your help. Lisa's dead.

1:15:44.415 --> 1:15:45.333
I know, dear.

1:15:45.667 --> 1:15:47.460
More of us are going to go
if you don't stick with it.

1:15:47.877 --> 1:15:49.295
Oh, Jenny.

1:15:49.712 --> 1:15:53.633
It's just that I'm not sure what to do
or how to do it, anymore.

1:15:54.092 --> 1:15:56.719
The harder I try,
the worse it gets for you and the others.

1:15:57.095 --> 1:15:59.138
No doc, you can't give up.

1:15:59.973 --> 1:16:01.933
I was wrong and you were right.

1:16:02.517 --> 1:16:03.643
Tell me what to do.

1:16:04.143 --> 1:16:06.521
- I'll need you to testify.
- Okay.

1:16:06.896 --> 1:16:09.566
I'll need you and the others
to tell your story to the outside.

1:16:09.899 --> 1:16:10.942
It'll be tough.

1:16:11.317 --> 1:16:13.528
They'll say you're lying,
but I'll back you.

1:16:13.861 --> 1:16:16.698
I'll go to the DA, the press,
whatever it takes, Jenny.

1:16:17.031 --> 1:16:18.533
We'll beat them right here.

1:16:20.410 --> 1:16:23.037
Sorry, Dr. Norton. Orders.

1:16:24.414 --> 1:16:25.623
I'm leaving.

1:16:30.378 --> 1:16:31.963
We'll get 'em, doc.

1:16:38.803 --> 1:16:40.096
Child abuse.

1:16:41.472 --> 1:16:43.182
That bitch
hasn't heard the last of me yet.

1:16:43.516 --> 1:16:45.101
She can't make it stick.

1:16:45.476 --> 1:16:48.563
We'll just say it's sour grapes
over her being fired.

1:16:49.063 --> 1:16:51.232
The commission won't interfere here.

1:16:54.402 --> 1:16:59.407
Bringing shocking accusations of torture
and inhuman conditions

1:16:59.741 --> 1:17:05.330
at Pridemore Juvenile Facilities,
Dr. Norton claims to have a chief witness

1:17:06.205 --> 1:17:08.124
willing to testify at the hearing.

1:17:09.709 --> 1:17:11.044
You've got one week.

1:17:11.461 --> 1:17:12.754
Clear?

1:17:14.339 --> 1:17:15.548
Crystal clear.

1:17:30.980 --> 1:17:33.650
You killer, you killer!

1:17:33.983 --> 1:17:35.777
You fucking murderer!

1:17:37.111 --> 1:17:38.446
Leave us alone.

1:18:20.113 --> 1:18:24.033
In light of the sensational circumstances
surrounding this case,

1:18:24.367 --> 1:18:27.328
I thought it best
to keep this hearing informal.

1:18:27.829 --> 1:18:29.414
And of course, private.

1:18:30.498 --> 1:18:34.252
I have reviewed your report, Dr. Norton,
and I must tell you

1:18:34.585 --> 1:18:37.880
that both the committee and myself
find it rather shocking

1:18:38.214 --> 1:18:39.966
and somewhat hard to believe.

1:18:41.217 --> 1:18:46.305
Warden Sutter also informed us
that you filed this report shortly

1:18:46.639 --> 1:18:50.184
after being dismissed of duty
at Pridemore Facilities.

1:18:50.727 --> 1:18:51.686
Is that correct?

1:18:52.019 --> 1:18:54.480
I assure you, your honor,
that I would not have made

1:18:54.814 --> 1:18:56.399
these accusations lightly.

1:18:56.733 --> 1:18:59.652
There are conditions and circumstances
at Pridemore

1:18:59.986 --> 1:19:02.113
which demand immediate attention.

1:19:02.572 --> 1:19:05.575
She just wants attention for herself,
your honor.

1:19:05.908 --> 1:19:08.161
I challenge Ms. Dawson's remark,
your honor,

1:19:08.494 --> 1:19:11.497
and if we might bring in my witness,
she will enlighten you

1:19:11.831 --> 1:19:13.958
and the board members
as to the seriousness

1:19:14.292 --> 1:19:15.710
of these accusations.

1:19:16.043 --> 1:19:17.378
That would be Ms. Williams?

1:19:17.920 --> 1:19:20.423
- Yes, your honor.
- Pardon me, your honor.

1:19:20.840 --> 1:19:22.717
Ms. Williams is unable to testify.

1:19:23.092 --> 1:19:24.302
What are you talking about?

1:19:24.761 --> 1:19:27.138
Where's Jenny?
What's happened to her?

1:19:27.638 --> 1:19:30.600
- She's not well.
- That is a lie.

1:19:30.933 --> 1:19:33.895
They are deliberately keeping the girl
away from testifying

1:19:34.228 --> 1:19:35.646
to protect themselves.

1:19:36.022 --> 1:19:39.108
Dr. Fisher examined the girl himself
this morning

1:19:39.442 --> 1:19:42.278
and said she was just too sick to leave.

1:19:43.112 --> 1:19:44.697
Dr. Fisher?

1:19:45.239 --> 1:19:47.241
Yes, your honor.
I examined the girl.

1:19:47.617 --> 1:19:49.911
She seemed a little weak,
almost delirious.

1:19:51.037 --> 1:19:52.705
Could be meningitis.

1:19:55.041 --> 1:19:58.586
However, your honor, present
are several girls from the same dorm.

1:19:58.961 --> 1:20:00.922
I'm sure you'll find them
just as cooperative.

1:20:37.750 --> 1:20:40.586
Hey.

1:20:40.920 --> 1:20:44.841
No. Guard, guard.

1:21:06.362 --> 1:21:08.656
Look, your honor,
we both love a good debate,

1:21:09.156 --> 1:21:11.033
but dinner's getting cold.
Let's wrap this up.

1:21:13.619 --> 1:21:14.912
Bring in the girls, please.

1:21:21.127 --> 1:21:22.628
Healthy girls, all.

1:21:25.464 --> 1:21:26.716
Good evening, young ladies.

1:21:27.049 --> 1:21:30.511
Now, I want you to understand
that this is just a simple meeting.

1:21:30.845 --> 1:21:34.015
No one is on trial and no one
is accused of anything.

1:21:34.390 --> 1:21:36.559
We simply want to ask you a few questions.

1:21:37.101 --> 1:21:38.519
Do you understand?

1:21:39.478 --> 1:21:40.730
Yes, sir.

1:21:41.564 --> 1:21:44.400
Dr. Norton here has made
some serious accusations

1:21:44.734 --> 1:21:47.737
concerning Matron Dawson
and the punishment she uses

1:21:48.070 --> 1:21:49.864
to discipline the girls in your dorm.

1:21:50.281 --> 1:21:52.658
Have any of you
ever been severely punished?

1:21:55.328 --> 1:21:58.080
- No, sir.
- No one ever been beaten?

1:21:59.749 --> 1:22:00.791
No, sir.

1:22:01.125 --> 1:22:04.128
Any of you ever had meals taken away
or a fire hose turned on you?

1:22:05.504 --> 1:22:07.131
- No, sir.
- Stop it.

1:22:07.465 --> 1:22:08.966
Stop it for God's sake.

1:22:09.342 --> 1:22:10.885
Can't you see they're scared?

1:22:11.218 --> 1:22:12.803
They're not going to tell you anything.

1:22:13.137 --> 1:22:14.180
They're frightened.

1:22:14.555 --> 1:22:17.141
Frightened of her
and of what she'll do if they talk.

1:22:17.600 --> 1:22:18.893
Tell them.

1:22:19.226 --> 1:22:23.564
Don't let her get away with this.
Tell them. Don't be afraid.

1:22:23.940 --> 1:22:25.942
Dr. Norton, you're out of order.

1:23:03.062 --> 1:23:05.356
Take her out, Claudia. Get her!

1:23:05.690 --> 1:23:07.108
You and me going for a little walk, bitch.

1:23:07.441 --> 1:23:08.317
Kill the bitch.

1:23:08.651 --> 1:23:10.152
Hold it right there,
unless you want this pig dead.

1:23:10.486 --> 1:23:11.988
- You'll never get away with this.
- Maybe not.

1:23:12.321 --> 1:23:15.074
If we go, you go with us.
Now, let's get to that meeting.
Come on.

1:23:27.878 --> 1:23:30.047
Freeze! Freeze right there.

1:23:31.257 --> 1:23:33.759
Go ahead, use it.

1:23:34.093 --> 1:23:35.511
You can't stop us all.

1:23:35.845 --> 1:23:37.388
They're bluffing.

1:23:37.722 --> 1:23:40.057
Don't be afraid. Shoot.

1:23:43.310 --> 1:23:44.562
Shoot, I tell you.

1:23:47.148 --> 1:23:49.692
She goes before I go.

1:23:50.818 --> 1:23:52.445
See you later, pig.

1:23:52.778 --> 1:23:54.196
Come on, let's go.

1:24:13.340 --> 1:24:14.550
Edna!

1:24:14.925 --> 1:24:17.803
Edna!

1:24:18.304 --> 1:24:19.722
What the hell is that?

1:24:20.056 --> 1:24:21.599
- It's the riot alarm!
- Oh, my God.

1:24:24.101 --> 1:24:26.145
My God, it's Jenny.

1:24:29.148 --> 1:24:31.317
All right, rumble!

1:24:33.611 --> 1:24:37.531
Edna, Edna, Edna,
Edna, Edna, Edna,

1:24:38.407 --> 1:24:45.122
Edna, Edna, Edna, Edna,
Edna, Edna, Edna.

1:24:46.499 --> 1:24:51.504
You've got 30 seconds
to get back to your dorm, or we open fire.

1:24:52.088 --> 1:24:53.506
We're not afraid of you anymore, Edna.

1:24:53.839 --> 1:24:56.550
We're going to that meeting
and we're going to tell it like it is.

1:24:56.884 --> 1:24:58.844
No one moves.

1:24:59.261 --> 1:25:00.888
- You can't kill us all.
- No way.

1:25:01.222 --> 1:25:03.724
Sooner or later, they're going to find out
about the beatings, and the tortures,

1:25:04.058 --> 1:25:05.976
and the murders.
It's all over, Edna.

1:25:06.310 --> 1:25:08.604
We're going in. Killer!

1:25:08.938 --> 1:25:12.483
Killer! Killer! Killer! Killer!

1:25:12.817 --> 1:25:16.070
Killer! Killer! Killer! Killer!

1:25:16.403 --> 1:25:19.907
Killer! Killer! Killer! Killer!

1:25:21.367 --> 1:25:24.203
- Fire!
- Killer! Killer! Killer!

1:25:24.537 --> 1:25:28.999
- Fire, damn it! Fire!
- Killer! Killer!

1:25:29.333 --> 1:25:32.670
Killer! Killer! Killer! Killer!

1:25:36.298 --> 1:25:38.008
You bitch!

1:26:28.392 --> 1:26:29.727
- Claudia.
- You going to kill her for us?

1:26:30.060 --> 1:26:32.021
You bet your ass, sister.

1:26:33.564 --> 1:26:37.985
Let's get the bitch!
Come on! Vengeance!

1:26:38.319 --> 1:26:39.987
Get her.

1:26:47.745 --> 1:26:51.665
Control! Complete control!

1:28:11.870 --> 1:28:14.081
You fucking bitch! Burn!

1:28:14.415 --> 1:28:16.792
Burn, you bitch! Burn!

1:28:32.850 --> 1:28:36.145
Control! Complete control!

1:28:46.071 --> 1:28:48.699
Control! Do you hear me?

1:28:49.033 --> 1:28:55.331
Complete control! Complete control!

1:28:55.664 --> 1:29:01.378
The name of the game is control.

1:29:01.712 --> 1:29:06.050
See you in hell, Edna.

1:30:17.204 --> 1:30:18.705
Get out of here. And I don't want to see

1:30:19.039 --> 1:30:20.582
that pretty mug of yours back here,
understand?

1:30:20.916 --> 1:30:22.209
You won't, I promise.
